First change directory to the folder where the source code is present.

To compile the code please run the following command
       make

To remove the existing executables run the following command
       make clean

The make command will create 5 executables with the following names
       Load
       Query
       Change
       Clean
       Print

Each executable can be run in the following format
       ./{ProgramName}

None of the programs expect any command line arguments to be passed when running them.
All the user inputs are promted inside the program.